project_descr: Enhancement of Living Standards in Andijan and Namangan regions

outputs.output_descr:
1. Authorities at all levels are better capable to formulate and execute development strategies/plans in a participatory manner in Andijan
2. Rural communities are able to participate in local development processes and  undertake self-help initiatives to  improve basic services in Namangan
3. Communities are better capable to undertake  private initiatives for equitable local economic development in Namangan

project_title: els in andijan and namangan regions
